data.description: The Rayburn by LGI Homes. This beautiful, two-story home features a soaring formal entryway, oversized bedrooms with walk-in closets, and an upstairs game room. Downstairs, the spacious and open layout boasts a huge living room, dining room and kitchen with breakfast bar. Designer extras include granite countertops in the kitchen, stainless-steel kitchen appliances, front yard landscaping and a fully fenced backyard. In addition, Bauer Landing features a gorgeous 3.5-acre community park.
